data.description: Welcome to your future home in beautiful Southern Colorado Springs! This charming property offers the perfect blend of spacious living, modern upgrades, and an enviable location with great access to military bases. With a large lot graced by mature trees, this residence exudes warmth and comfort from the moment you arrive. As you step through the front door, you'll be welcomed into your first of multiple living areas, this one with massive ceilings that create an airy and inviting ambiance. This open and bright space seamlessly flows into the well-appointed kitchen (stainless steel fridge included) and dining area, making it an ideal spot for hosting gatherings and creating lifelong memories. The owners have poured their love and attention into this home, adding numerous upgrades to enhance its appeal. The flooring has been thoughtfully updated in much of the home. The backyard has been transformed into an oasis with a retaining wall, perfect for relaxing and entertaining. What's more, this home is equipped with solar panels that will come paid off, saving you money on your energy bills. All the bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs, ensuring privacy and a peaceful retreat. A second living room adjacent to the kitchen provides versatility in its use, whether you need an extra entertainment area or a cozy place to unwind. The basement offers a world of possibilities. With its generous space, you can choose to leave it as a vast multi-use area or use it as a fourth bedroom - there's already a closet! To keep you comfortable year-round, this home also features air conditioning.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. It's the perfect blend of a well-loved home, upgrades for modern living, and a superb location in Southern Colorado Springs. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the charm and convenience this home has to offer!
